    "content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><A name=OLE_LINK5></A><A name=OLE_LINK4><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>军营集训是户外独立拓展项目之一。以全封闭式军事化训练特点而著称。日常生活均采用部队的军事化生活管理办法。纪律与服从是军营集训的第一要旨。</SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>企业军营集训，更重要的是根据不同类型的企业需求，设置各类拓展项目与教育引导内容。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>将企业要达成的培训目标，成为军营集训目标之一。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>金牌拓展以十余年人力资源管理经验，将员工的素质教育巧妙的融合于拓展项目中，使两者达成有机的结合，这是金牌拓展的特色与优势。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>附：中国人民解放军纪律条令（总则）</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>纪律条令文（</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>Discipline Regulations<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>）：规定军队纪律的法规。由军队最高领导机关或领导人颁发全军执行。军人遵守纪律的准则，军队维护纪律、实施奖惩的依据。目的在于培养军人高度的组织性和纪律性，执行命令，服从指挥，令行禁止，协调一致，巩固和提高战斗力。世界上许多国家都根据本国的社会制度和军队建设的需要与传统，制定了不同形式的维护纪律的法规。如东欧一些国家的军队有纪律条令，美国军队有《军事统一法典》，英国军队有《军队法令》等。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第一章 总 则</SPAN></B></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第一条 为了维护和巩固</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'></SPAN></SPAN><A href='http://baike.baidu.com/view/24050.htm' target=_blank><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; TEXT-DECORATION: none; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: windowtext; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; text-underline: none'>中国人民解放军</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'></SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>的纪律，正确实施奖惩，保证军队的高度集中统一，加强革命化、现代化、正规化建设，巩固和提高战斗力，根据有关法律的规定，结合军队实际，制定本条令。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第二条 本条令是中国人民解放军维护纪律、实施奖惩的基本依据，适用于中国人民解放军</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'></SPAN></SPAN><A href='http://baike.baidu.com/view/2896467.htm' target=_blank><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; TEXT-DECORATION: none; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: windowtext; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; text-underline: none'>现役军人</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'></SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>和单位，以及参战、支前的预备役人员。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4'><SPAN style='mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: 